action.description: The recommendation of the committee(s) on HHS is to ADVISE AND CONSENT to the nomination(s).  The votes in HHS were as follows: 4 Aye(s): Senator(s) San Buenaventura, Aquino, Hashimoto, Keohokalole; Aye(s) with reservations: none ; 0 No(es): none; and 1 Excused: Senator(s) Fevella.
